sources.title: Kung Fu Killer 2 | FULL MOVIE | 2008 | Action, Martial Arts | David Carradine
sources.description:
To avenge the murder of his Wudang Grandmaster, White Crane, a Caucasian monk and spiritual master of the martial arts, infiltrates the Shanghai underground, where he forms an unusual bond with a New York lounge singer and her gangster boss. In this twisted den of crime, Crane must cross the line between true justice and cold-blooded revenge.

Starring:
David Carradine
Daryl Hannah
Jimmy Taenaka
Osric Chau
Lim Yu-Beng
Christian Joel Lee
Yan Yan Wu

2008
Directed by Philip Spink
